    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty heavy take. so you're saying it's basically impossible for a country to have a shared national identity that isn't based on excluding others? if that's the case, then what's actually the alternative for keeping a diverse society from falling apart without relying on those tribal instincts?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
